data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Apartment
data.value: Inomobolo yeflethi yakho ayikho okanye ayifumaneki. Nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for invalid apartment number.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Charset
data.comment: The error message when data is in charset that is not supported by address verification.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.DoubleConfirm
data.value: Asikwazi ukuqiniseiksa idilesi yakho. Nceda uqinisekise idilesi yakho ngoku uze ucinezele "<Okulandelayo>".
data.comment: The error message when address verification system requires user to double confirm the address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.ID
data.value: Inombolo yeflethi ayichananga. Nceda ulungise igama lakho.
data.comment: The error message for invalid apartment ID.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Insufficient
data.value: Idilesi ayifanelekanga. Nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for insufficient information for address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.InvalidData
data.value: Idilesi ayifanelekanga, nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message when data is missing for address verification.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Multiple
data.value: Idilesi ayifanelekanga, nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for invalid address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Pobox
data.value: Ibhokisi yeposi ayixhaswa. Nceda ulungiselele idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for POBOX.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.PostalCode
data.value: Ikhowudi yeposi ayifunyanwa. Nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for invalid postal code.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Route
data.value: Inkonzo yohambiso echaziwe ayifunyanwa okanye ayikho kwindawo okuyo. Nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Street
data.value: Igama lesitrato alifunyanwa kwikhowudi yeposi. Nceda ulungise idilesi yakho.
data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail
data.value: Asikwazi ukugunyazisa uhlobo lwentlawulo. Nced uqinisekise ukuba inkcazelo ichanile, okanye usebenzise enye indlela yentlawulo ukuba ufuna ukuqhubeka ufumana umyalezo, nceda qhangamshelana neziko lezimali.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail2
data.value: Kuye kwakho ingxaki ebudeni bokuhlolwa kwesixhobo sakho sentlawulo. Nceda udibane nenkonzo yabathengi ukuze ufumane uncedo.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails. Probably, the PI is rejected by risk.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.BR
data.value: Olu tshintshiselwano alukwazanga ukugunyaziswa. Nceda uqinisekise inkcazelo yakho. Amanye amakhadi entlawulo asenokungamkelwa kweli qonda, kule meko, sikhuthaza ukuba usebenzise elinye ikhadi lentlawulo. Ukuba ingxaki iyaqhubeka, usenokuqhagamshela iziko lezemali lakho.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Brazil. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.MX
data.value: Olu tshintshiselwano alukwazanga ukugunyaziswa. Nceda uqinisekise inkcazelo yakho. Amanye amakhadi entlawulo asenokungamkelwa liqonda lentlawulo ngenxa yeepolisi zokhuseleko ezibekiweyo. Ukuba ingxaki iyaqhubeka, usenokuqhagamshela iziko lezemali lakho.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Mexico. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.CardUsedMuiltipleTimes
data.value: Indlela yakho yokuhlawula yongezelelwe kwiindlela ezininzi zeakhawunti. Nceda zama enye indlela.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card is used too many times.

data.name: Literal.Error.CcExpired
data.value: Ikhadi lakho letyala liphelelwe. Nceda ukhethe usuku lokuba lokuphelelwa kwikamva.
data.comment: The error message shown when the credit card is expired.

data.name: Literal.Error.CcNumberInvalid
data.value: Inombolo yakho ye-credit card ayisasebenzi. Nceda ufake inombolo esebenzayo ye-credit card.
data.comment: The error message shown when the credit card number is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdBankCodeInvalid
data.value: Inombolo yakho yerouting ayifanelekanga, nceda ufake inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit bank code is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdBranchCodeInvalid
data.value: Ikhowudi yakho yokuhlela ayifanelekanga, nceda ufake inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit branch code is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdNumberInvalid
data.value: Inombolo yeakhawunti yakho ayifanelekanga, nceda ufake inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit account number is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.AccountIdInvalid
data.comment: The error message is shown when the billable account id is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.AccountLocked
data.comment: The error message is shown when the billable account is locked or disabled.

data.name: Literal.Error.EnterValidInfo
data.comment: The error message shown when user enters invalid information.

data.name: Literal.Error.EnterValidInfo2
data.value: Inkcazelo yentlawulo yakho ayisasebenzi. Ukuba uqhubeka ufumana lo myalezo, zama enye indlela yokuhlawula okanye udibane nenkonzo yabathengi ukuze ufumane uncedo.
data.comment: The error message shown when user enters invalid information.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAddress
data.value: Idilesi yakho ayifanelekanga, nceda ufake inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the address is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAddress2
data.value: Idilesi yakhe ayikho. Nceda uqiniseke ukuba inkcazelo yakho yedilesi ichanile.
data.comment: The error message shown when the address is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidCity
data.value: Isixeko sakho asifanelekanga, nceda ufake enye inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the city is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidPhoneType
data.value: Ingcombolo yefowuni yakho ayisebenzi, nceda ungenise ingcaciso esebenzayo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the phone type is not valid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidState
data.value: Iphondo lakho alifanelekanga, nceda ufake inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the state is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidZipcode
data.value: Ikhowudi yakho ayifanelekanga, nceda ufake inkcazelo efanelekileyo.
data.comment: The error message shown when the zipcode is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.PhoneNumberRequired
data.comment: The error message shown when the phone number is missing.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiAlreadyExists
data.value: Asikwazi ukongeza uhlobo lwentlawulo ngenxa yokuba sele lukho kwiakhawunti yakho. Nceda uzame ngenye indlela.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card that is already added.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiAlreadyExists2
data.value: Asikwazi ukufaka inkquboyakho yokuhlawula. Nceda uqinisekise ukuba ayikhange khe ifakwe kule akhawunti. Ukuba uqhubeka ufumana lo myalezo, zama enye indlela yokuhlawula okanye uqhagamshelane nenkonzo yabathengi ukuze ufumane uncedo.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card that is already added.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiBanned
data.value: Indlela yakho yokuhlawula iyekisiwe. Nceda uzame ngenye indlela.
data.comment: The error message shown when the PI is banned.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiExceedMaxOwnership
data.value: Le nkcazelo osidlulisele yona sele isetyenziswa ziiakhawunti ezininzi. Ncea ungene kwenye iakhawunti okanye idilesi yeposi.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add a pi which has been used by other accounts for many times.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiLimitExceeded
data.value: Asikwazi ukongeza ukhetho lwentlawulo. Sebenzisa ukhetho lwentlawulo, okanye ushenxise ukhetho lwentlawulo.
data.comment: The error message shown when paper check last name is not correct.

data.name: Literal.Error.SaInIntermediateStatus
data.value: Asikwazi ukugqibezela isicelo sakho ngoku ngenxa yokuba ikhadi lakho letyala sele litsalelwa olunye urhumelo namhlanje. Nceda usebenzise elinye ikhadi okanye uzame kwakhona kamva.
data.comment: The error message shown when the PI is in intermediate status.

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.AR
data.value:
Ukuze sikulungiselele imveliso okanye inkonzo kufuneka uyile iakhawunti yomsebenzisi. Ngalo lonke ixesha ulungiselela indlela entsha yentlawulo kwimveliso okanye inkonzo sinokulungiselela isaziso esilandelayo size siqokelele isivumelwano esivela kuwe ngaphambi kokuba uqhubeke. Ebudeni bexesha lenjongo yokuyilwa kweakhawunti kuza kufuneka unikezele ngeenkcukacha zakho zobuqu ezifana: negama lakho, idilesi, inombolo yomnxeba, idilesi yeimeyili, inombolo yekhadi letyala nenombolo yeakhawunti yebhanki. Sinokuqokelela idilesi yeIP kunye neID yesixhobo sakho size sizinxulumanise nenkcazelo yakho yobuqu siyile iakhawunti okanye xa usongeza indlela yentlawulo entsha.
Ndivumela ukuba iMicrosoft Corporation, kunye nezinye iinkampani zayo, ukuba zisebenzise inkcazelo yam yobuqu endiyinikezileyo, ngokwemiqathango yoMthetho 25, 326, ICandelo 5 ngokwenjongo yokuthumela iimpapasho kunye/okanye ezentengiso ezimayelana nokunikezela iimveliso kunye/okanye iinkonzo. Nditsho oku ngokuvumelana neMthetho 25, 326, ICandelo 6, ndazisiwe ngako ngokuzithandela.
Ukusilela ukulungiselela le nkcazelo kuphumelela kuphela ekusebenziseni imveliso neenkonzo ezilungiselelwe kwiphepha lewebhu. Xa ndidlulisela inkcazelo yam, ndiza kube ndidlulisela imvume yokuba kugcinwe loo nkcazelo kwiMicrosoft Corporation emiselwe eRedmond, WA 98052. Umnikazi wenkcazelo yobuqu unelungelo lokusebenzisa amalungelo akho ngaloo nkcazelo ngaphandle kwentlawulo nonqumano olungaphezulu kweenyanga ezintandathu ngaphandle kokuba ulungiselele ubungqina beengenelo ekwenzeni oko kulungiselelwe nguMthetho 25, 326, ICandelo 14, ICandelo elingaphantsi 3. Igunya elilawula uMthetho 25, 326 ubizwa ngokuba yiARGENTINI DIRECTORATE OF PERSONAL DATA PROTECTION kwaye unika amandla okwenza izivumelwano nomkhalazi okanye isicelo esibekwe ngokwamalungelo okusilela ukuhambisana nenkcazelo yokhuseleko.
Unokungena okanye utshintshe inkcazelo yakho yobuqu kwi: https://billing.microsoft.com. Ukuba ukhetha ukutshintsha inkcazelo yakho yobuqu apha uyavuma ukuba iMicrosoft Corporation iqokelele ize igcine inkcazelo yakho njengoko kuchazwe ngasentla.
Ngokuyila iakhawunti ucinezela iqhosha elithi “Ndiyavuma” ngezantsi ngaloo ndlela uvumelana neMicrosoft Corporation ngenkcazelo yakho yobuqu nangokuvumelana neMicrosoft Corporation ekuqokeleleni kwabo nasekuthumeleni njengoko kuboniswe apha.

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.HU
data.value:
Ukuze sikwazi ukukuzisela imveliso kunye nenkonzo kufuneka uzenzele i akhawunti eyeyakho yabasebenzisi. Thuba ngalinye usenza isixhobo sentlawulo entsha yemveliso okanye inkonzo siyakuthumelela inkcazelo elandelayo kunye sifumane nemvume yakho ngaphambi kokuqhubeka phambili. Ngethuma nangesibakala sokwenza i akhawunti okanye ufaka isixhobo sentlawulo kuya kufuneka ubonise uhlobo lokuzazisa ngenkcukacha zakho ezifana nezi: igama lakho, idilesi, inombolo yomnxeba, idilesi ye imeyile, inombolo yekrediti khadi okanye inomblo yekhadi lakho lebhanki. Sinokulanda idilesi ye IP kunye nesazisi sesixhobo ukuze sizihlanganise nenkcukacha zakho zobuqu ozinikezileyo ngethuba lokwenza i akhawunti okanye xa asongeza isixhobo sentlawulo esitsha.
Ezinkcukacha zobuqu zikwazisayo ziyakuqokelelwa zize ngokukhawuleza zidluliselwe xa i akhawunti ivuliwe, ngendlela ekhuselekileyo engaphakathi ku Ezinkcukacha zobuqu zikwazisayo ziyakuqokelelwa zize ngokukhawuleza zidluliselwe xa i akhawunti ivuliwe, ngendlela ekhuselekileyo engaphakathi ku Microsoft Corporation e United States ukuze kuqhutywe uthengiselwano nokuze sizise imveliso kunye nenkonzo kuwe. Le nkcazelo isenokugcinwa isetyenziswe ngoxa kusavumelekile ngokwasemthethweni. Microsoft Corporation akayi kusebenzisa inkcukacha zakho zokuzazisa ezifumeneke apha ngenjongo ezizezinye ngaphandle kwezidandalaziswe apha, kuquka kodwa kungapheleliswanga kwimicimbi yentengiso.
Microsoft Corporation nikezela ngenkcukacha zakho zobuqu zokuzazisa komnye umntu. Inkcazelo yakho inikezelwa komnye umntu xa kusenziwa oko kuya kufaneleka ukusebenza ngentengo yakho, kulandelwe imisebenzi yezomthetho, kuphendulwe izicelo, kukhuselwe urhwaphilizo okanye kwenziwe ngokuvumelana nemithetho karhulumente.
Unokungena okanye utshintshe inkcazelo yakho yobuqu kwi: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Ukuba kungafuneka utshintshe inkcazelo yobuqu ufumana apha isigunyaziso esikuvumela iMicrosoft Corportation ukuba iqokelele ngokukhawuleza ize ithumele inkcazelo yakho yobuqu oyitshintshileyo njengokuba kuchaziwe ngasentla.
Ngokuyila iakhawunti ucinezela iqhosha elithi “Ndiyavuma” ngezantsi uze uvumelane nokuba iMicrosoft Corporation ilungiselele inkcazelo yakho yobuqu nesigunyaziso esivela kuwe ekubeni iMicrosoft iqokelele, ithumele ize yabelane nabanye abantu ngeenkcazelo yakho yobuqu njengokuba injalo apha.

Microsoft Corporation akayi kusebenzisa inkcukacha zakho zokuzazisa ezifumeneke apha ngenjongo ezizezinye ngaphandle kwezidandalaziswe apha, kuquka kodwa kungapheleliswanga kwimicimbi yentengiso.
Microsoft Corporation nikezela ngenkcukacha zakho zobuqu zokuzazisa komnye umntu. Inkcazelo yakho inikezelwa komnye umntu xa kusenziwa oko kuya kufaneleka ukusebenza ngentengo yakho, kulandelwe imisebenzi yezomthetho, kuphendulwe izicelo, kukhuselwe urhwaphilizo okanye kwenziwe ngokuvumelana nemithetho karhulumente.
Unokungena okanye utshintshe inkcazelo yakho yobuqu kwi: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Ukuba kungafuneka utshintshe inkcazelo yobuqu ufumana apha isigunyaziso esikuvumela iMicrosoft Corportation ukuba iqokelele ngokukhawuleza ize ithumele inkcazelo yakho yobuqu oyitshintshileyo njengokuba kuchaziwe ngasentla.
Ngokuyila iakhawunti ucinezela iqhosha elithi “Ndiyavuma” ngezantsi uze uvumelane nokuba iMicrosoft Corporation ilungiselele inkcazelo yakho yobuqu nesigunyaziso esivela kuwe ekubeni iMicrosoft iqokelele, ithumele ize yabelane nabanye abantu ngeenkcazelo yakho yobuqu njengokuba injalo apha.

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.KR

Inkcazelo yakho idluliselwa xa kuyimfuneko ukuze kuproseswe utshintshiselwano lwakho, kuhanjiswana neenkqubo zomthetho, siphendula izicelo, sikhusela urhwaphilizo okanye zihambisana nemithetho karhulumente.
Unokungena okanye utshintshe inkcazelo yakho yobuqu apha: https://billing.microsot.com. Ukuba ukhetha ukutshintsha inkcazelo yakho ngaloo ndlela ulungiselela isivumelwano kunye ne-Microsoft Corporation ukuze iqokelele ize ngokukhawuleza ithumele inkcazelo ebhalwe ngasentla.
Ngokuyila iakhawunti nangokucinezela iqhosha elithi “Ndiyavuma” ngezantsi ngokuvumelana ne-Microsoft Corporation nenkcazelo yakho yobuqu nesivumelwano sokuqokelela se-Microsoft, nokuthumela nokwabelana nenkcazelo yakho yobuqu echaziwe nezinye iinkampani njengokuba kubekwe kwiNgxelo yaBucala ye-Microsoft Online ebhalwe apha: http://privacy.microsoft.com/ko-kr

data.name: Literal.CreditCheck.SSNInfo
data.value: Siqokelela iNombolo Yokhuseleko Yentlalo (SSN) evela kuwe size sabelane ngayo nabanye abantu abafanelekileyo ukuze bahlole amatyala akho ukuze sikwazi ukwazi enoba ungafumana luphi unikezelo. Sisebenzisa imilinganiselo yobuxhakaxhaka ukuze sikuncede ukhuseleke ekungeneni ngokugunyazisiweyo, usebenzisa okanye usazisa iSSN. Sithumela iSSN kwinethiwekhi ekhuselekileyo evaliweyo ngaphambi kokuthunyelwa. Asigcini iSSN emva kokukugqiba ukuhlola amatyala akho, nakuba ukugcina ukwaziwa kwakho okukodwa ngenjongo yolawulo oluqhelekileyo. Siza kugcina amanqaku akho amatyala nenye inkcazelo esiyikhuphe njengenxalenye yokuhlolwa kwamatyala akho ukuba nje kufanelekile ukugqiba ukuthenga kwakho nokuhlola size sikhusele urhwaphilizo.
data.comment: Info for SSN.

data.value: Ngokusebenzisa lo myalelo, ukhethe ukuTsalwa kweMali Ngqo njengendlela ohlawula ngayo. Ukusebenzisa kwakho ukuTsalwa kweMali Ngqo kuxhomekeke ekuvumeni kwakho nasekuthobeleni le mimiselo. Ugunyazisa uMicrosoft Payments Ltd. ("thina" okanye "sisonke") ukuba acele intlawulo kwibhanki yakho ngemali oyityala uMicrosoft. Kumele uqinisekise ukuba: (i) unikezele ngedilesi ye-imeyile eyiyo ukwenzela imbalelwano kunye nezaziso; (ii) ibhanki yakho iyakwamkela ukuqokelelwa kwemali etsalwa ngqo; (iii) unemali eyaneleyo nangaliphi na usuku lokutsala; (iv) umyalelo wakho awurhoxiswanga (ngaphandle kwanjengalapha ezantsi) okanye awuyekiswanga. Ukuphanza ukuthobela le mimiselo nokunokukhokelela kukungahlawuli, akukukhululi kwisibophelelo sakho sokuhlawula nayiphi na imali oyityalayo nekufuneka uyihlawulile. Nceda uqhagamshelane nathi ukuze urhoxise lo myalelo okanye ukhethe enye indlela yokwenza intlawulo. Siyakuwurhoxisa umyalelo wakho xa sifumene isaziso sakho. UkuTsalwa kweMali Ngqo kuyafumaneka ngokwembono yethu, kwaye ukuba kuyafumaneka, siyakuqhagamshelana nawe ukwenza amanye amalungiselelo.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement.New
data.value: Ngokubhalisa okanye ngokukhetha iakhawunti yakho yebhanki ukuba ibe yindlela ohlawula ngayo, ugunyazisa u-Microsoft (okanye abameli bakhe) ukuba badebhithe kanye okanye ngakumbi imali eyitotali (kuquka irhafu efunekayo, iimali neendleko zokuthumela) yento oyithengileyo okanye iindleko zokurhuma (ngokuhambisana nemiqathango yenkonzo oyirhumelayo) kwiakhawunti yakho (kwaye, ukuba kuyimfuneko, akhredithe kwibhanki yakho kanye okanye ngakumbi ukuze alungise iimpazamo, abuyise imali okanye injongo efanayo), kwaye uyaligunyazisa iziko leakhawunti yakho yebhanki ukuba litsale ezo debhithi okanye lamkele ezo khredithi. Uyaqonda ukuba olu gunyaziso luza kuhlala lunamandla kwaye lusebenza de ukhuphe inkcazelo yeakhawunti yakho yebhanki kwiakhawunti yakho yakwa-Microsoft okanye kweka-Skype.

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsg
data.value: Abathengi abasebenzisa iibrawuza zewebhu ngaphandle kwe-IE (i-Internet Explorer) abasayi kukwazi ukubhalisela iinkonzo ezintsha ze-Azure ngenxa yomba wokufakelwa kwe-ActiveX. Nceda usebenzise i-IE okanye i-VM (i-Virtual Machine) kunye ne-IE ukuze ubhalise. Emva kokuba ibhalisiwe indlela yokuhlawula, uza kukwazi ukusebenzisa ezinye iibrawuza zewebhu zeenkonzo ze-Azure. Sicela uxolo ngokukulibazisa.

Nceda usebenzisa i-Internet Explorer ukuze ungene. Emva kokungena, unokusebenzisa nayiphi na ibrawuza. Uxolo ngokukuhlupha.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.SubHeader
data.value: Ngoku ungalusebenzisa ugunyaziso lweentlawulo zika-Microsoft ozivume kwangaphambili naphi na apho u-PayPal akhoyo xa uhlawula ku-Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.US
data.value: Sebenzisa u-PayPal kwixesha elizayo xa uhlawula kwa-Microsoft. Ukuba unayo ibhalansi ku-PayPal, loo bhalansi iza kusetyenziswa kuqala, kwanokuba ukhethe indlela oyithandayo yokuhlawula. Ukuba awukhethanga indlela yokuhlawula oyithandayo, kuza kusetyenziswa indlela yokuhlawula yakho eyidifolthi. Ukuba indlela yokuhlawula oyithandayo okanye eyidifolthi iphelelwe lixesha okanye ikhatyiwe, u-PayPal uza kutsala kwenye indlela yakho yokuhlawula. Ungayiseta okanye uyitshintshe indlela ohlawula ngayo, okanye urhoxise olu gunyaziso nanini na kwiiSethingi zakho ku-Paypal.com. De usete indlela yokuhlawula kwiiSethingi zakho, indlela yokuhlawula esetyenziswayo iza kulandela iipolisi zokuhlawula eziku-PayPal.com.
data.comment: Text for United States, Canada, Brazil

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.DE
data.value: Ukuze kongezwe ukhuseleko, kungenzeka kufuneke ukuba siqinisekise iakhawunti yakho yebhanki. Kuxhomekeka kwibhanki yakho, le nto ingathatha usuku ukuya kweziyi-3.

data.value: Xa kuyimfuneko, abathengi abakwi-EU bafanele banikele ngeenkcukacha zenombolo yobhaliso yabo ye-VAT esebenzayo. Ukungayenzi loo nto kunganefuthe kwindlela ephathwa ngayo loo invoyisi ikhutshwe ngu-Microsoft xa kufikwa kwi-VAT.

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line1
data.value: Irhafu yezinto neenkonzo yaseNew Zealand (NZ GST) eyi-15% iyatsalwa kwiinkonzo ezinqumla imida zerimowuthi nakwizinto ezingaphathekiyo ezinikelwa ngabavelisi abangengabo abemi kumntu ohlala eNew Zealand ngaphandle kokuba lishishini elibhaliswe kwi-GST. Umvelisi umele amthathe umntu ozifumanayo ngokungathi akabhaliswanga ngaphandle kokuba loo mntu uzifumanayo wazisa umvelisi ukuba ubhalisile aze aveze inombolo yakhe yobhaliso ye-NZ GST.

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Text
data.value: Uyamvumela u-Microsoft ukuba adlulisele imiyalelo yentlawulo yakho ka-PayPal ku-PayPal ngezinto ozithengileyo ngqo ku-Microsoft okanye kulowo uza kufumana intlawulo usebenzisa u-Microsoft. Ukuba unebhalansi ku-PayPal, iza kusetyenziswa kuqala. Ukuba indlela ohlawula ngayo oyithandayo okanye eyidifolthi ikhatyiwe okanye iphelelwe lixesha, kuza kutsalwa komnye umthombo wakho wemali. Uyamvumela u-PayPal ukuba abelane ngeenkcukacha zonaniselwano luka-PayPal noMicrosoft. Ukwabelana ngeenkcukacha zakho zonaniselwano zika-PayPal kwenza u-Microsoft azi ukuba intlawulo yakho iphumelele na, ancedise ekuphumezeni unaniselwano lwakho kwaye anikele ngeerisithi zentlawulo ezichazwe kwiPolisi Yokugcinwa Kweemfihlelo Ka-PayPal. Uyalela uPayPal ukuba athathe izicelo zentlawulo ezithunyelwe ngu-Microsoft njengezigunyaziswe nguwe ngokweSivumelwano Somsebenzisi Sakwa-PayPal. Ukuba uhlawula ngekharensi engeyiyo ikharensi eyintloko kwiAkhawunti Ka-PayPal yakho, u-PayPal uza kuyitshintsha loo mali esebenzisa amaxabiso asebenza ngelo xesha. Ungalurhoxisa olu gunyaziso okanye utshintshe umthombo wemali owuthandayo nanini na kwiakhawunti yakho yakwa-PayPal. Ukuba urhoxisa imvume yakho yokusebenzisa uPayPal ku-Microsoft, uPayPal angamazisa u-Microsoft.
data.comment: PayPal Scenario Strings - Agreement text for the update Paypal billing agreement page
